      <DefaultText>You scan the pile of offerings for a long time, but everything there is worthless.

You are about to turn away when the Speck appears at your elbow. "I know what you seek," she whispers. "Your sire's offering is there" She points to a spot near the bottom of the pile.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>69</ID>
      <DefaultText>Sure enough, you can see it now - the sharpened edge of a metallic device, half-buried under silver trinkets and the moldering arm of some unidentifiable beast. Its unusual shape evokes a feeling of familiarity. You're certain that this was the offering left by the Changing God... and you suspect that it's a Merecaster. </DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
